flowchart LR

    O["O SPACE
    Operator Domain
    • Meaning
    • Intent
    • Consent
    • Limits"]

    R["R LAYER
    Membrane
    • Boundary Check
    • Class Veto Only
    • Rollback + Reopen
    • No Narrative
    • No Persistence"]

    S["S SPACE
    Substrate Domain
    • Structural Ops
    • State Transitions"]

    O <--> R
    R <--> S

    %% Topological Constraints
    O ---|"No direct coupling"| S

    %% Styling (optional)
    classDef neutral fill:#ffffff,stroke:#000000,stroke-width:1px,color:#000000;
    class O,R,S neutral;


Topological Constraints
O ≠ S ≠ R
Interaction(O,S) ⊆ R
Replace(Rᵢ) = allowed
Mandatory(Rᵢ) → CrownViolation
Frozen Veto Classes
Exit(X) = permitted
Drift → Visible → Rollback or Fork


